# newShippingMethods

**Instance Property**

A list of shipping methods that are available to the updated shipping contact.

## Declaration

```swift
sequence <ApplePayShippingMethod> newShippingMethods;
```

## Discussion

Supply a list of shipping methods that apply to the updated shipping contact, if the shipping methods changed. See [doc://com.apple.applepayontheweb/documentation/ApplePayontheWeb/ApplePayShippingMethod].

## Updating shipping contact properties

- **errors**: A list of custom errors to display on the payment sheet.
- **newLineItems**: An optional list of updated line items.
- **newTotal**: The new total that results from a change in the shipping contact.
